step_data.thought: To modify the inventory quantity of the Blue T-Shirt, I need to first focus on the quantity textbox which currently has a value of '150'. I will clear this field and then fill it with the new desired quantity. After filling in the new quantity, I will need to save the changes. Therefore, the next action is to clear the quantity field.
